that I could be with Princess

290
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:37,940
to serve her again.

291
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:41,060
Your Majesty still entrusts me with the duty.

292
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:42,420
I...

293
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:44,460
You did make mistakes

294
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:46,620
but you’re always

295
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,740
kindhearted.

296
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,820
Despite what happened,

297
00:17:52,820 --> 00:17:54,140
you risked your life

298
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:55,740
and saved Mrs. Yang

299
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:56,820
from being burned.

300
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,220
So I’m willing to trust you.

301
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:02,140
I also believe

302
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,580
you can protect Huirou,

303
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:05,380
respect her husband

304
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:09,740
and minimize the damage.

305
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:15,340
You won’t disappoint me,

306
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:16,980
will you?

307
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:23,860
Yes, Your Majesty.

308
00:18:26,780 --> 00:18:27,780
You can

309
00:18:28,580 --> 00:18:31,020
go back with Huirou today.

310
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:40,260
I, Sima Guang, request a meeting.

311
00:18:40,380 --> 00:18:42,860
I need answers from Your Majesty.

312
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:46,900
Your Majesty.

313
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:52,100
Censor Sima Guang

314
00:18:52,100 --> 00:18:53,420
is outside waiting to be summoned.

315
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:56,180
Tell him the court is adjourned.

316
00:18:56,580 --> 00:18:57,980
Now isn’t the time to raise advice.

317
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:00,140
Leave it till tomorrow.

318
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:03,660
I already said that but he refused to leave

319
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:05,700
and insisted on meeting Your Majesty today

320
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:08,100
to address this issue.

321
00:19:10,980 --> 00:19:11,940
What is it about?

322
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:18,380
About Your Majesty allowing Mr. Liang

323
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:19,740
to go back to Princess’s Mansion.

324
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:25,940
I, Sima Guang, request a meeting.

325
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:29,380
I need answers from Your Majesty.

326
00:19:31,620 --> 00:19:32,580
Send Zhang Maoze in.

327
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:34,180
Yes.

328
00:19:37,620 --> 00:19:38,460
You may leave.

329
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:40,940
Be discreet

330
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:42,550
when you go back with Huirou.

331
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:48,500
I, Sima Guang, request a meeting.

332
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:51,700
I need answers from Your Majesty.

333
00:20:10,140 --> 00:20:10,860
Your Majesty.

334
00:20:13,860 --> 00:20:15,460
Go to the Cabinet and tell Han Qi

335
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:19,180
I appointed Zongshi Chief of the Imperial Clan,

336
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,460
but he refused to accept it

337
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:23,460
in the name of mourning for Duke Pu, Yunrang.

338
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:26,900
Taotao also begged Empress repeatedly

339
00:20:27,620 --> 00:20:30,180
to let them leave the Capital.

340
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:33,220
I watched Zongshi grow up.

341
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:35,820
Taotao is Empress’s adopted daughter.

342
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:36,980
I care about them

343
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:40,260
and don’t want to burden them

344
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:42,500
with the court or the nation against their will.

345
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:49,220
I, Sima Guang, request a meeting.

346
00:20:49,540 --> 00:20:52,700
I need answers from Your Majesty.

347
00:21:00,420 --> 00:21:01,180
Yes.

348
00:21:11,420 --> 00:21:12,460
Tell Sima Guang

349
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:14,300
to wait for me at the Pavilion of Talent.

350
00:21:15,140 --> 00:21:15,740
Yes.

351
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:18,540
It can’t be changed again!

352
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:20,380
Zongshi only refused to take that position

353
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:21,740
for fear of His Majesty’s change of heart

354
00:21:21,740 --> 00:21:23,860
and public opinion.

355
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,900
If His Majesty hesitates at this moment...

356
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:28,580
Is he at his chamber?

357
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,900
I’m going to see him now.

358
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:32,940
He’s at the Pavilion of Talent

359
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:35,700
meeting with Censor Sima Guang.

360
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:38,700
Sima Guang?

361
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:41,660
What is he there for?

362
00:21:42,820 --> 00:21:45,100
Princess’s family business.

363
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:49,580
I already advised Your Majesty

364
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:51,700
that former manager of Princess’s Mansion,

365
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:52,660
Eunuch Liang Huaiji

366
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:54,500
not be called back for his unforgivable sin,

367
00:21:55,980 --> 00:21:57,300
but was denied.

368
00:21:58,180 --> 00:21:59,100
Just now,

369
00:21:59,740 --> 00:22:01,020
I heard he was allowed

370
00:22:01,020 --> 00:22:02,700
to serve Princess again.

371
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:06,660
That news aroused chatter

372
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:07,700
and bombed all officials.

373
00:22:10,340 --> 00:22:12,300
You have eyes and ears everywhere

374
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,780
and you’re well-informed.

375
00:22:14,540 --> 00:22:15,940
Paying attention to Your Majesty’s family business

376
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:17,100
is our duty.

377
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,940
We dare not to slack.

378
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:26,660
I should thank you then.

379
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:40,060
It’s said during the reign of Emperor Taizong,

380
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:41,580
whenever his son Duke Yan made mistakes,

381
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:43,780
Yan Tan would advise against it.

382
00:22:44,860 --> 00:22:46,900
Later on, servants incited Duke Yan

383
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:48,100
to fake an illness.

384
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:49,460
who then took a sick leave for over a month.

385
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:51,700
His nurse told Emperor Taizong

386
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,380
that Duke Yan wasn’t physically ill.

387
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,420
Yao Tan was so strict with him

388
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:57,100
that made him depressed

389
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:58,580
for lacking freedom.

390
00:22:58,780 --> 00:23:00,340
Emperor Taizong was infuriated,

391
00:23:00,780 --> 00:23:02,980
saying “I selected decent officials to teach him

392
00:23:02,980 --> 00:23:04,180
to be virtuous

393
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:06,860
yet he faked his illness

394
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,740
just to get rid of them for freedom.

395
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:09,940
That is intolerable.

396
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:12,100
My son is too young

397
00:23:12,540 --> 00:23:13,900
to come up with such a scheme.

398
00:23:13,900 --> 00:23:15,460
You must have taught him that”.

399
00:23:15,900 --> 00:23:18,020
Then Emperor Taizong had his son’s nurse

400
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:19,780
beaten dozens of times in the backyard

401
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:22,500
and comforted Yao Tan.

402
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:26,060
Didn’t Emperor Taizong

403
00:23:26,700 --> 00:23:28,260
love his son?

404
00:23:29,460 --> 00:23:31,140
He did. That’s all the more reason

405
00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:32,900
to discipline him.

406
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:36,940
Indulging his every whim unconditionally

407
00:23:37,100 --> 00:23:38,620
was harming him.

408
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:41,700
Right now, that eunuch is driving a wedge

409
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:42,820
between Princess and her husband.

410
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:45,220
Your Majesty should follow the precedent

411
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:46,300
to discipline Princess

412
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:47,500
and punish her servant

413
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:50,580
so that she’ll right her wrong

414
00:23:51,140 --> 00:23:53,540
and make up with her husband.

415
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:19,940
Perhaps in Your Majesty’s eyes,

416
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:22,380
as noble as Princess is,

417
00:24:22,780 --> 00:24:24,500
she’s still a woman

418
00:24:25,180 --> 00:24:26,220
whose fault

419
00:24:26,300 --> 00:24:28,100
won’t shake the court or the state.

420
00:24:28,940 --> 00:24:30,700
Her mistake isn’t as serious

421
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:32,700
as Duke Yan’s.

422
00:24:39,740 --> 00:24:40,700
As far as I’m concerned,

423
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:44,220
she’s Your Majesty’s eldest daughter

424
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:47,420
who’s under constant scrutiny by the public.

425
00:24:48,740 --> 00:24:49,980
Princesses’ actions

426
00:24:50,380 --> 00:24:51,700
are also recorded in history

427
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:53,180
for future generations to study.

428
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:56,700
Your Majesty’s aunt

429
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:59,140
Elder Princess Xianmu of Qi

430
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,260
is filial and humble

431
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:02,580
who treats her husband’s family

432
00:25:02,580 --> 00:25:03,620
dutifully.

433
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:06,620
She adores her husband without jealousy.

434
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:07,980
Even till this day,

435
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:09,580
she’s a role model for women

436
00:25:09,620 --> 00:25:12,060
in the eye of the public.

437
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:15,660
In my humble opinion,

438
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,940
Your Majesty should adopt

439
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:19,940
Emperor Taizong’s teaching in educating Princess.

440
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:21,860
Princess should treat her husband the same way

441
00:25:22,220 --> 00:25:24,860
Princess Xianmu treats hers.

442
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:29,260
I don’t want

443
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:30,380
any of my daughters

444
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:32,900
to live as my aunt.

445
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:40,260
I’m confused, Your Majesty.

446
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,180
You aren’t a father

447
00:25:44,060 --> 00:25:45,060
so you don’t understand.

448
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:55,020
I don’t have any children

449
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:58,220
but I do know emperors aren’t commoners.

450
00:25:59,140 --> 00:26:02,020
Emperors should set good examples to the public.

451
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:05,260
Your Majesty is pampering Princess so much

452
00:26:05,260 --> 00:26:06,340
that she’s above the law and order

453
00:26:07,060 --> 00:26:09,340
and acts wildly as she pleases.

454
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:12,780
She even threatened Your Majesty with her life,

455
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:15,900
humiliated her husband and abandoned morals.

456
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,380
If Your Majesty covers for her,

457
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:19,940
how can virtues

458
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:21,740
be promoted across the nation

459
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,780
and carried on by later generations?

460
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:31,500
I’m not a saint as Emperor Yao or Shun.

461
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:35,340
I can’t set a good example of everything.

462
00:26:41,540 --> 00:26:42,940
Scholar of the Academy of Literature,

463
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:46,020
Consultant of the Cabinet, Han Qi

464
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:47,300
requests to see Your Majesty for an urgent matter.

465
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:59,580
I beg Your Majesty to exile Liang Huaiji

466
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,980
and send him back to where he belongs.

467
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:04,100
If those around Princess

468
00:27:04,180 --> 00:27:05,780
ask Your Majesty to call him back,

469
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:07,500
they’re bad influences on her

470
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:09,660
and should all be punished and sent away.

471
00:27:09,980 --> 00:27:12,380
Replace them

472
00:27:12,580 --> 00:27:14,100
with kind and upright servants.

473
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:20,140
What’s your urgent matter?

474
00:27:24,180 --> 00:27:25,420
I’m here for Zongshi’s refusal

475
00:27:25,820 --> 00:27:28,940
to be Chief of the Imperial Clan.

476
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:30,860
I don’t think

477
00:27:32,060 --> 00:27:35,020
Your Majesty should allow it.

478
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:43,900
Your Majesty, a decree can’t be taken back.

479
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,100
I believe

480
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:47,820
he refused to take up that post

481
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:49,220
because he was afraid that Your Majesty

482
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:50,140
was reluctant to appoint him.

483
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:52,100
Zongshi is considerate and filial.

484
00:27:52,660 --> 00:27:54,940
He doesn’t want Your Majesty

485
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:56,100
to choose him under officials’ pressure.

486
00:27:59,140 --> 00:28:00,180
I didn’t know

487
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:02,020
you know him so well.

488
00:28:05,580 --> 00:28:09,540
If Your Majesty suspects our relationship,

489
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:11,940
I’m open to investigation.

490
00:28:13,580 --> 00:28:15,300
Those are all my honest thoughts.

491
00:28:16,380 --> 00:28:18,980
They must be heard even if they’ll get me killed.

492
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:26,540
All these years,

493
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:29,660
have I ever killed anyone for raising advice?

494
00:28:30,340 --> 00:28:32,300
Death is uncalled for.

495
00:28:34,820 --> 00:28:36,180
If that’s what Zongshi wants,

496
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:37,260
let’s not push him.

497
00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:42,540
This isn’t your personal matter

498
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:44,980
and shouldn’t be judged with feelings.

499
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,340
Your Majesty has already

500
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:49,380
issued the decree

501
00:28:49,980 --> 00:28:51,740
to announce to the public

502
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:55,860
that Zongshi will lead the Imperial Clan.

503
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,460
His appointment concerns the entire state.

504
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:00,500
How can it be withdrawn?

505
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:05,100
Well then,

506
00:29:05,860 --> 00:29:07,380
you should think of a way

507
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:09,100
to persuade him.

508
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,500
Your Majesty, Her Highness has arrived.

509
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:33,220
More presents from your family?

510
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,340
They aren’t from my family

511
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:40,060
but Taotao,

512
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:43,260
including toys for princesses

513
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:45,900
and...

514
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:50,380
a long letter for you by Zongshi.

515
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:08,620
It’s not that he doesn’t want it

516
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,820
but he fears that I don’t want to give it to him.

517
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:13,620
He thinks I’m testing him

518
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:16,580
so he dares not to show a hint of eagerness.

519
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:22,460
But you do intend to give it to him.

520
00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:28,980
But now,

521
00:30:30,420 --> 00:30:32,180
I don’t want them to feel too easy.

522
00:30:37,060 --> 00:30:38,300
Humans aren’t saints.

523
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,660
I can’t always be fair.

524
00:30:45,540 --> 00:30:46,900
I’m impartial

525
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:50,180
towards my own daughter.

526
00:30:52,140 --> 00:30:53,940
But are those officials pushing me so hard

527
00:30:55,860 --> 00:30:57,780
all to uphold justice?

528
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:05,700
They intend to mold me

529
00:31:05,980 --> 00:31:07,940
into the so-called saint they defined

530
00:31:08,980 --> 00:31:10,460
and my daughter

531
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:12,500
the saintess.

532
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,940
To them,

533
00:31:16,260 --> 00:31:17,300
Zongshi, of course,

534
00:31:17,340 --> 00:31:18,500
isn’t a human of flesh and blood, either.

535
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:21,660
They forbid us

536
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:23,460
from having personal feelings.

537
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:26,220
Is that really good for the nation?

538
00:31:28,340 --> 00:31:29,980
Is it good for the people

539
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:31,580
or just to meet

540
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:32,860
their obsession?

541
00:31:36,380 --> 00:31:37,220
I think

542
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:40,020
some anxiety is good for them.

543
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:42,020
Put Huirou’s and Zongshi’s matters together

544
00:31:42,020 --> 00:31:43,540
and discuss them freely.

545
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:45,460
Call me

546
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:48,020
unfair and selfish if they want.

547
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:55,100
Officials do hope

548
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:58,740
all imperial clansmen are like Buddhas

549
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:01,620
who have no feelings or desires

550
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:04,780
and can only be worshiped by the public.

551
00:32:05,780 --> 00:32:07,060
They can’t be selfish.

552
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:12,120
Just now, I was reading

553
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:13,500
Learn to Overcome Weaknesses by Mr. Yan.

554
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:17,420
According to him,

555
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:20,540
overindulging family members is wrong.

556
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:22,260
Yes.

557
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:24,700
I indulge Huirou.

558
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:28,700
Officials fear that I’ll cross the line for her

559
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:29,660
and dislike her even more.

560
00:32:30,900 --> 00:32:32,860
But I can’t stop spoiling her

561
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:34,580
or protecting her.

562
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:36,820
I won’t change my mind.

563
00:32:38,460 --> 00:32:39,700
In this world,

564
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:42,140
nobody can be completely selfless.

565
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:45,780
A role model

566
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:48,100
shouldn’t fake selflessness

567
00:32:48,820 --> 00:32:50,460
but balance the needs of his own

568
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:52,620
and others’.

569
00:32:58,860 --> 00:32:59,660
Princess,

570
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:02,540
from now on, I won’t leave your mansion

571
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:04,540
without the order.

572
00:33:05,660 --> 00:33:06,380
But

573
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:09,180
I won’t enter your chamber, either.

574
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:12,140
Please allow me

575
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:14,900
to keep you company

576
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,220
and protect you from afar.

577
00:33:18,140 --> 00:33:19,380
That way,

578
00:33:20,260 --> 00:33:22,500
I may be able to stay with you longer.

579
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:25,820
I hate myself of losing my mind

580
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:27,100
and control of myself

581
00:33:27,980 --> 00:33:28,860
and staying too close to you before,

582
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:30,500
causing you to suffer so much.

583
00:33:52,140 --> 00:33:53,540
Zongshi still refuses

584
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:54,980
to take up that post.

585
00:34:04,740 --> 00:34:06,060
It’s understandable.

586
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:08,900
Those twists and turns

587
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,060
must have taken a toll on him.

588
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:14,380
We can

589
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:16,500
repeat our request to His Majesty.

590
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:18,740
His Majesty

591
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,780
is well aware of the situation.

592
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:23,380
He’s set his mind on Zongshi

593
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:25,460
but refuses to crown him the Crown Prince.

594
00:34:27,180 --> 00:34:29,340
His Majesty has his concerns.

595
00:34:32,460 --> 00:34:33,340
About what?

596
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:39,020
Crowning Zongshi won’t change anything.

597
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:41,180
Officials will still be loyal to His Majesty.

598
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:43,580
If the Crown Prince is disobedient,

599
00:34:43,580 --> 00:34:45,420
he’ll be condemned.

600
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:46,380
What is His Majesty concerned about?

601
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:51,060
What if officials

602
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:53,020
find His Majesty’s decision unacceptable

603
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:55,740
and press him to change his mind?

604
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,560
You mean that matter about princess?

605
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,840
About that,

606
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:06,000
Sima Guang

607
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,720
is overly stubborn.

608
00:35:09,160 --> 00:35:11,760
It’s true that the public looks up to Princess

609
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:14,340
and wishes her to be flawless.

610
00:35:15,180 --> 00:35:16,740
If she really is a saintess

611
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:19,300
that all parents attempt to

612
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:22,180
model their daughters on, that will be great.

613
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:24,940
But she’s an ordinary girl after all.

614
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:26,940
She is unable to be a role model.

615
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,860
Because of Sima Guang,

616
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:32,820
this matter is bubbling up

617
00:35:33,020 --> 00:35:35,700
that everyone is finding fault with princess,

618
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:37,220
and even

619
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:40,300
His Majesty.

620
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:44,500
Maybe

621
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:46,940
that’s exactly

622
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:48,340
what Sima Guang

623
00:35:48,820 --> 00:35:50,060
intends to achieve.

624
00:35:51,580 --> 00:35:53,140
His Majesty and Princess

625
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:55,940
aren’t as saintly as he expected.

626
00:35:56,740 --> 00:35:58,060
As a censor,

627
00:35:58,620 --> 00:36:00,380
he is encouraging the public to monitor

628
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:01,460
and criticize His Majesty

629
00:36:01,820 --> 00:36:03,500
to prevent him from abusing his power.

630
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:05,500
As a result,

631
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:08,180
His Majesty feels more repressed by censors.

632
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:15,950
Fresh vegetables!

633
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,760
Princess,

634
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,200
Prince Consort is outside.

635
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,040
I don’t want to see him.

636
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:32,480
= Yun Guo’er =

637
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,320
Princess,

638
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,440
please spare him

639
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,600
ten minutes

640
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:37,680
to speak his mind.

641
00:36:39,120 --> 00:36:40,560
I promise

642
00:36:41,160 --> 00:36:42,800
that he won’t offend you, Princess.

643
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:51,920
Jiaqing Zi, you may come in.

644
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:15,680
Your birthday is next month.

645
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:19,040
I’d like to give you my present in advance

646
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:21,320
which is also

647
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:23,480
the last thing

648
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:24,520
I can give you.

649
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:26,520
I believe

650
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:30,040
you’ll need it

651
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:31,680
and like it.

652
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:03,000
I used to think too highly of myself

653
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,760
that I could protect you,

654
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,640
look after you

655
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:08,760
and make you happy.

656
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:11,640
But I didn’t realize until later

657
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:14,640
that I’m the source

658
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:16,040
of your pain.

659
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:19,720
I was a fool

660
00:38:20,640 --> 00:38:21,640
and I hurt you a lot.

661
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:27,600
I’ve applied to be transferred outside the Capital

662
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:28,440
for failing to serve you.

663
00:38:29,200 --> 00:38:29,960
That way,

664
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,280
you can go back to the palace

665
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:33,680
and reunite with your family.

666
00:38:36,080 --> 00:38:37,280
Also, I begged my brother

667
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:38,920
to seek permission from His Majesty after I leave

668
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,040
to allow me...

669
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,760
Allow me to divorce you.

670
00:38:48,600 --> 00:38:52,000
What I want to say

671
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,320
is all in this letter.

672
00:38:59,000 --> 00:38:59,640
You...

673
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,960
You’re willing to divorce me?

674
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,880
I wish you

675
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:15,040
a worry-free

676
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,440
and happy life without me.

677
00:40:00,020 --> 00:40:02,820
= Divorce Letter =

678
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:39,440
Minister Han, you once said

679
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,480
His Majesty had asked you

680
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,600
to look for my brother.

681
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:45,520
There was no news about him

682
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,360
until later I was told

683
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:50,240
that he became a eunuch in the palace.

684
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:53,880
That was unfair to my family!

685
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,680
His Majesty didn’t know that.

686
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:03,680
When I found out

687
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:06,960
that both His Majesty

688
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:08,560
and Princess liked him,

689
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:10,400
I decided to let him be.

690
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:14,440
But Heaven is cruel to him.

691
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:15,960
Right now, censors

692
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,400
are calling him an evil influence

693
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,760
and demanding that he should be executed.

694
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:22,880
Minister Han,

695
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:27,120
I have my own family and business

696
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:29,160
but nothing

697
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,840
is more important

698
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:32,680
than my brother’s life.

699
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:34,840
If they’re going to kill him

700
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:36,840
in the name of dispelling evil,

701
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:39,200
I’ll do my best

702
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,600
to show the world

703
00:41:40,720 --> 00:41:41,760
how much

704
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:42,920
my brother suffered

705
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,320
under the reign of His Majesty.

706
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:53,200
Are you threatening me?

707
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,360
When you were still a commoner,

708
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,200
you stood outside my house

709
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:07,480
to protect my family from street bullies.

710
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:11,440
Although misfortune still befell us,

711
00:42:11,720 --> 00:42:13,800
I’m always grateful

712
00:42:14,100 --> 00:42:15,180
for your help.

713
00:42:17,660 --> 00:42:19,580
Even after encountering corrupted officials myself,

714
00:42:20,140 --> 00:42:22,420
I still believe most officials

715
00:42:22,660 --> 00:42:24,700
are as righteous as you.

716
00:42:28,980 --> 00:42:30,860
You’ve become Prime Minister

717
00:42:33,970 --> 00:42:36,540
while my brother’s life is at risk.

718
00:42:38,180 --> 00:42:41,100
Is he really a poison to the state?

719
00:42:44,100 --> 00:42:45,020
Minister Han,

720
00:42:47,180 --> 00:42:48,300
if he isn’t,

721
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:50,460
please help him!

722
00:43:07,690 --> 00:43:17,350
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

723
00:43:18,690 --> 00:43:27,030
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

724
00:43:29,870 --> 00:43:34,590
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

725
00:43:35,570 --> 00:43:39,730
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

726
00:43:41,170 --> 00:43:46,650
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

727
00:43:46,650 --> 00:43:51,440
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

728
00:43:55,100 --> 00:44:00,740
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

729
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,650
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

730
00:44:06,150 --> 00:44:11,910
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

731
00:44:11,910 --> 00:44:17,000
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

732
00:44:17,430 --> 00:44:22,360
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

733
00:44:22,980 --> 00:44:27,830
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

734
00:44:28,520 --> 00:44:33,670
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

735
00:44:34,170 --> 00:44:39,210
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

736
00:44:39,750 --> 00:44:43,820
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

737
00:44:45,290 --> 00:44:49,930
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

738
00:44:50,950 --> 00:44:56,110
♪ The howling wind ♪

739
00:44:56,480 --> 00:45:00,550
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

740
00:45:02,030 --> 00:45:06,950
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

741
00:45:07,610 --> 00:45:12,830
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

742
00:45:13,250 --> 00:45:18,530
♪ The howling wind ♪

743
00:45:18,820 --> 00:45:23,720
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

744
00:45:24,310 --> 00:45:31,020
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
